  <synthesis-reference/>
  <indication>It is used in cortisporin-TC ear drops to help penetration of active ingredients through cellular debris for its antibacterial action.</indication>
  <pharmacodynamics>Thonzonium bromide causes dispersion and penetration of cellular debris and exudate, thereby promoting tissue contact of the administered medication.</pharmacodynamics>
